I should have become
Senwell’s general manager earlier.

589
00:30:44,800 --> 00:30:45,800
I hope to have your cooperation

590
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:47,660
at work in the future.

591
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:52,340
As the interim chairman,

592
00:30:53,650 --> 00:30:56,060
I am in charge of the company’s major decisions

593
00:30:56,710 --> 00:30:57,920
instead of cooperating with you.

594
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:04,620
Ziqian,

595
00:31:06,990 --> 00:31:09,250
you have gone too far

596
00:31:09,850 --> 00:31:11,490
in your loyalty and protection of the Shans.

597
00:31:12,280 --> 00:31:13,900
I hope you can have a sober mind.

598
00:31:14,810 --> 00:31:17,180
Otherwise, you will be cheated like a fool.

599
00:31:18,590 --> 00:31:19,480
What do you mean?

600
00:31:21,070 --> 00:31:23,450
Chairman Xu, your father,

601
00:31:23,470 --> 00:31:25,350
used to be one of
the three shareholders of the company.

602
00:31:26,390 --> 00:31:28,680
Even if he had a very good relationship
with Shan Yaolong,

603
00:31:29,190 --> 00:31:31,620
he wouldn’t have transferred
all his shares to others.

604
00:31:32,590 --> 00:31:33,890
Don’t you feel very strange?

605
00:31:34,760 --> 00:31:36,670
Haven’t you have any suspicion?

606
00:31:36,950 --> 00:31:38,800
Don’t make irresponsible remarks
to instigate conflicts.

607
00:31:39,870 --> 00:31:40,750
Not everybody

608
00:31:40,950 --> 00:31:43,290
prioritizes benefits like you in the world.

609
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:45,110
Not everybody is so kindhearted and naive

610
00:31:45,930 --> 00:31:47,370
like you in the world, either.

611
00:31:49,890 --> 00:31:50,630
My father

612
00:31:51,050 --> 00:31:52,650
voluntarily transferred his shares.

613
00:31:53,030 --> 00:31:55,360
Friendship and liberty are
the most important to him,

614
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:57,250
so it is with me.

615
00:31:57,400 --> 00:31:58,070
Ziqian,

616
00:31:59,580 --> 00:32:00,940
I am just considering it

617
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:02,160
from your perspective.

618
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:03,670
Don’t be too silly,

619
00:32:04,870 --> 00:32:06,330
or you will be cheated.

620
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:10,250
Don’t be too shameless,

621
00:32:11,040 --> 00:32:12,340
or you will be punished.

622
00:32:37,430 --> 00:32:39,070
Do I have to tell Senwell

623
00:32:39,090 --> 00:32:41,770
that Shan Junhao is at Guanmei Fishing Village.

624
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:46,830
No.

625
00:32:47,190 --> 00:32:48,230
I can’t.

626
00:32:49,140 --> 00:32:51,160
If Shan Junhao is back to Senwell,

627
00:32:51,630 --> 00:32:53,910
he will dismantle my Guanmei Hotel right away.

628
00:33:10,970 --> 00:33:11,910
Folks.

629
00:33:19,910 --> 00:33:21,340
Lots of money.

630
00:33:21,800 --> 00:33:22,820
Also excavators.

631
00:33:34,710 --> 00:33:35,490
Zhang Minghan,

632
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:36,680
what on earth are you doing?

633
00:33:37,470 --> 00:33:38,180
Mr. Tang,

634
00:33:39,950 --> 00:33:42,080
don’t you remember that it’s the farewell day

635
00:33:42,740 --> 00:33:43,680
for Guanmei Inn today?

636
00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:45,520
Farewell day?

637
00:33:46,070 --> 00:33:47,340
Do you want to dismantle Guanmei Inn?

638
00:33:48,820 --> 00:33:49,730
Boss,

639
00:33:50,170 --> 00:33:51,320
will it be dismantled?

640
00:33:51,600 --> 00:33:52,900
Our business is going up now.

641
00:34:02,120 --> 00:34:03,140
Hello, Mr. Tang?

642
00:34:03,160 --> 00:34:03,890
Director Xu.

643
00:34:05,010 --> 00:34:06,150
Didn’t you agree to

644
00:34:06,170 --> 00:34:08,030
give me a grace period if I told you

645
00:34:08,290 --> 00:34:09,290
the truth about Shan Junhao?

646
00:34:09,950 --> 00:34:11,500
But Senwell already dispatched people

647
00:34:11,520 --> 00:34:13,600
to dismantle Guanmei Inn
before Mr. Shan was back to Senwell.

648
00:34:13,980 --> 00:34:14,930
Dismantle your inn?

649
00:34:15,430 --> 00:34:15,980
Who is that?

650
00:34:18,460 --> 00:34:19,350
Mr. Zhang.

651
00:34:21,710 --> 00:34:22,460
I will be there right away.

652
00:34:22,480 --> 00:34:23,330
OK.

653
00:34:25,560 --> 00:34:26,210
What’s up?

654
00:34:26,570 --> 00:34:28,500
Zhang Minghan and his people are going
to dismantle Guanmei Inn.

655
00:34:28,520 --> 00:34:29,110
What?

656
00:34:29,480 --> 00:34:29,950
Go.

657
00:34:31,260 --> 00:34:32,270
Dear villagers,

658
00:34:34,500 --> 00:34:36,440
I know your biggest concern.

659
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:39,370
Senwell has tripled the compensation.

660
00:34:40,290 --> 00:34:42,920
Not every real estate developer can do this.

661
00:34:44,250 --> 00:34:46,270
It shows Senwell’s sincerity to you all.

662
00:34:46,870 --> 00:34:48,570
You can take away the money right away.

663
00:34:49,300 --> 00:34:49,890
But

664
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:53,950
you must sign a contract.

665
00:34:54,850 --> 00:34:55,860
Hello, Ye Qianyu?

666
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:57,180
Guanmei Inn is in big trouble.

667
00:34:57,200 --> 00:34:57,830
Come here right away.

668
00:34:58,030 --> 00:34:59,270
So much money, am I dreaming?

669
00:34:59,440 --> 00:35:01,120
Triple the standard compensations?

670
00:35:01,140 --> 00:35:02,180
Yes.

671
00:35:02,200 --> 00:35:02,840
Zhang Minghan,

672
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,590
you can’t do this.

673
00:35:04,890 --> 00:35:05,680
Mr. Tang,

674
00:35:06,760 --> 00:35:08,180
you are not the decision-maker.

675
00:35:08,990 --> 00:35:09,990
Dear all villagers,

676
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:11,900
you are the decision-makers.

677
00:35:12,570 --> 00:35:13,990
Anybody who signs the contract today

678
00:35:14,330 --> 00:35:15,660
will enjoy discounts

679
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:17,620
to buy a property

680
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:19,200
from Senwell.

681
00:35:23,370 --> 00:35:24,040
I will sign it!

682
00:35:25,820 --> 00:35:26,410
Donglu,

683
00:35:27,070 --> 00:35:28,010
don’t sign it!

684
00:35:28,350 --> 00:35:29,150
Mr. Tang,

685
00:35:29,170 --> 00:35:30,600
I’m not so silly to refuse money.

686
00:35:30,770 --> 00:35:32,370
How much are those dilapidated properties worth?

687
00:35:32,660 --> 00:35:34,870
It is a windfall indeed.

688
00:35:35,610 --> 00:35:36,560
Let go of me.

689
00:35:42,160 --> 00:35:42,970
He really signed it.

690
00:35:46,200 --> 00:35:46,840
Thanks!

691
00:35:47,030 --> 00:35:49,000
Thanks so much!

692
00:35:50,900 --> 00:35:52,860
Real money!

693
00:35:56,210 --> 00:35:57,260
Triple the standard compensations!

694
00:36:11,600 --> 00:36:12,210
Tonghao,

695
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:12,890
hurry up.

696
00:36:13,330 --> 00:36:14,130
Tie it up.

697
00:36:19,050 --> 00:36:19,660
Qianyu,

698
00:36:20,140 --> 00:36:21,010
what are you doing?

699
00:36:21,030 --> 00:36:22,300
Senwell plans to dismantle Guanmei.

700
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,730
I will resist them to the end.

701
00:36:24,910 --> 00:36:25,540
Tonghao,

702
00:36:25,560 --> 00:36:26,370
what are you busy with?

703
00:36:26,390 --> 00:36:27,810
Tie it up. Or it will be too late.

704
00:36:27,830 --> 00:36:29,120
Senwell has prepared for it.

705
00:36:29,140 --> 00:36:30,850
We must find a countermeasure.

706
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,130
What is that?

707
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:39,120
White dolphin?

708
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:40,820
I have prepared the diving suit.

709
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:41,910
Let’s go now.

710
00:36:44,450 --> 00:36:45,720
You had the same idea.

711
00:36:45,980 --> 00:36:47,380
What on earth are you talking about?

712
00:36:47,670 --> 00:36:48,280
Let’s go.

713
00:36:50,010 --> 00:36:50,560
Let’s go.

714
00:36:52,370 --> 00:36:53,350
Oh.

715
00:36:54,570 --> 00:36:56,160
Folks, don’t sign the contract.

716
00:36:56,180 --> 00:36:57,610
Don’t sign the contract.

717
00:36:57,630 --> 00:36:58,350
Dear all,

718
00:36:58,830 --> 00:36:59,870
don’t sign the contract.

719
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:01,100
Dear all folks,

720
00:37:01,900 --> 00:37:03,370
we are not selling properties.

721
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:06,570
It is our home that our ancestors

722
00:37:07,450 --> 00:37:09,430
have operated and maintained with their life.

723
00:37:13,430 --> 00:37:14,280
Without the home,

724
00:37:15,490 --> 00:37:17,900
we will all become homeless roamers.

725
00:37:19,260 --> 00:37:20,960
Butterball,

726
00:37:20,980 --> 00:37:22,880
I can repay all my debts

727
00:37:22,900 --> 00:37:25,000
with so much money.

728
00:37:31,430 --> 00:37:32,240
Mr. Tang,

729
00:37:34,340 --> 00:37:36,530
you are no longer the owner of Guanmei Inn,

730
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:38,530
nor can you represent the villagers.

731
00:37:38,870 --> 00:37:40,270
Please don’t be a troublemaker.

732
00:37:40,520 --> 00:37:42,350
You are not just hampering
the progress of Senwell’s project,

733
00:37:42,550 --> 00:37:44,090
but undermining the villagers’ benefits.

734
00:37:45,230 --> 00:37:46,390
They can live a better life

735
00:37:47,110 --> 00:37:49,270
with the money, right?

736
00:37:50,200 --> 00:37:51,230
Yes.

737
00:37:52,960 --> 00:37:54,180
Don’t be so stubborn.

738
00:37:54,200 --> 00:37:55,370
It is good for nobody.

739
00:37:55,390 --> 00:37:56,890
Let’s get the money together

740
00:37:56,910 --> 00:37:59,300
and it is good for all.

741
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:00,130
Yes.

742
00:38:00,150 --> 00:38:01,200
Exactly.

743
00:38:01,220 --> 00:38:01,850
Tang Shunming,

744
00:38:01,870 --> 00:38:03,530
stop undermining our interests.

745
00:38:03,550 --> 00:38:04,890
Your inn is about to collapse

746
00:38:04,910 --> 00:38:06,010
and it is useless at all.

747
00:38:06,200 --> 00:38:08,450
We can buy a big apartment in the downtown
with the compensations

748
00:38:08,470 --> 00:38:09,840
and it is a good deal.

749
00:38:09,860 --> 00:38:10,890
Yes.

750
00:38:10,910 --> 00:38:12,370
It is good to sign the contract.

751
00:38:12,390 --> 00:38:13,470
Take a second thought.

752
00:38:13,490 --> 00:38:14,640
Yes.

753
00:38:26,650 --> 00:38:27,570
Stop it!

754
00:38:27,590 --> 00:38:28,680
What are you going to do?

755
00:38:33,390 --> 00:38:34,330
Mr. Tang.

756
00:38:39,350 --> 00:38:41,350
If you want to dismantle my Guanmei Inn,

757
00:38:41,370 --> 00:38:43,690
just run over my body first.

758
00:38:43,710 --> 00:38:44,340
Mr. Tang.

759
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:46,350
Mr. Tang.

760
00:38:46,490 --> 00:38:47,890
What a stubborn butterball!

761
00:38:47,910 --> 00:38:49,740
Just give up Guanmei Inn.

762
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:51,690
You don’t have to risk your own life.

763
00:38:52,520 --> 00:38:54,030
Without Guanmei,

764
00:38:54,490 --> 00:38:56,330
my family’s business
developed in three generations

765
00:38:56,670 --> 00:38:58,330
will be completely destroyed.

766
00:38:59,620 --> 00:39:01,430
What is the point of my survival?

767
00:39:01,450 --> 00:39:02,150
Mr. Tang,

768
00:39:03,300 --> 00:39:04,630
you have threatened us

769
00:39:04,650 --> 00:39:05,860
with your suicide once.

770
00:39:06,520 --> 00:39:08,530
It is too stupid to play this game.

771
00:39:08,910 --> 00:39:10,740
Please don’t waste our time.

772
00:39:12,610 --> 00:39:13,250
Folks!

773
00:39:13,610 --> 00:39:15,220
Sign the contract and get the money right away.

774
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:16,510
Go and sign it!

775
00:39:17,010 --> 00:39:17,680
Yes.

776
00:39:18,910 --> 00:39:19,840
What are you doing?

777
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:24,420
Don’t sign it!

778
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:27,280
Don’t sign it!

779
00:39:27,900 --> 00:39:30,710
Stop! Don’t sign it! Listen to me!

780
00:39:31,200 --> 00:39:34,120
Don’t sign it! Don’t sign it!

781
00:39:35,600 --> 00:39:38,150
Don’t sign it!

782
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:46,470
Qianyu, come here right away! Big troubles!

783
00:39:46,600 --> 00:39:48,770
Butterball is besieged and attacked.

784
00:39:52,210 --> 00:39:53,760
Delay it?

785
00:40:06,160 --> 00:40:06,760
It is here!

786
00:40:42,540 --> 00:40:43,230
Qianyu,

787
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:46,650
take care!

788
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:52,540
Please take care!

789
00:41:00,590 --> 00:41:01,630
Let’s go.

790
00:41:01,780 --> 00:41:02,400
OK.

791
00:41:06,430 --> 00:41:11,170
Don’t sign it!

792
00:41:12,750 --> 00:41:14,090
Calm down!

793
00:41:14,110 --> 00:41:15,220
Don’t sign it!

794
00:41:17,130 --> 00:41:18,330
Don’t sign it!

795
00:41:18,350 --> 00:41:19,360
No more jostle!

796
00:41:20,530 --> 00:41:21,590
Don’t come here!

797
00:41:22,790 --> 00:41:23,430
Listen,

798
00:41:23,450 --> 00:41:24,370
don’t come any further!

799
00:41:25,580 --> 00:41:26,730
I have heart diseases.

800
00:41:27,420 --> 00:41:28,780
Anybody who comes over and knocks me down

801
00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:30,020
will have to take the responsibility.

802
00:41:32,120 --> 00:41:35,080
Forget him. He is a liar.

803
00:41:35,630 --> 00:41:37,130
Delay it?

804
00:41:37,430 --> 00:41:38,520
No more jostle!

805
00:41:41,760 --> 00:41:43,120
Calm down.

806
00:41:43,420 --> 00:41:44,250
Tang Shunming,

807
00:41:44,850 --> 00:41:45,680
give me the contract.

808
00:41:45,700 --> 00:41:46,270
No.

809
00:41:46,740 --> 00:41:47,390
Give me!

810
00:41:48,290 --> 00:41:48,800
No.

811
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:49,770
Give me.

812
00:41:50,020 --> 00:41:50,730
I will tear it.

813
00:41:50,750 --> 00:41:51,580
You won’t have the courage.

814
00:41:52,090 --> 00:41:53,170
I will show you the courage!

815
00:41:53,190 --> 00:41:54,600
I challenge you to do that. You are a coward!

816
00:41:54,620 --> 00:41:56,290
I am a real coward if I don’t tear it!

817
00:41:56,600 --> 00:41:58,170
You are a coward
because you won’t have the courage!

818
00:41:58,190 --> 00:41:59,950
I… I will tear it!

819
00:42:01,900 --> 00:42:03,250
I will!

820
00:42:03,880 --> 00:42:04,710
Again!

821
00:42:05,800 --> 00:42:07,160
Stop it!

822
00:42:07,910 --> 00:42:09,120
Tang Shunming!

823
00:42:09,140 --> 00:42:10,250
Again!

824
00:42:10,430 --> 00:42:11,110
Stop it,

825
00:42:11,130 --> 00:42:12,600
or I will tear you into pieces!

826
00:42:12,620 --> 00:42:13,170
Stop it!

827
00:42:13,970 --> 00:42:14,820
No fighting!

828
00:42:18,180 --> 00:42:19,300
Why are you…

829
00:42:19,320 --> 00:42:20,050
Get away!

830
00:42:20,520 --> 00:42:21,320
Give it to me!

831
00:42:21,640 --> 00:42:22,200
Beat you!

832
00:42:22,220 --> 00:42:23,060
I will beat you!

833
00:42:42,040 --> 00:42:47,200
♪ Distance between us ♪

834
00:42:50,490 --> 00:42:55,510
♪ Seems short yet long ♪

835
00:42:56,630 --> 00:43:00,690
♪ Heartfelt words are exchanged in diaries ♪

836
00:43:00,710 --> 00:43:04,310
♪ There are no secrets between us ♪

837
00:43:04,880 --> 00:43:12,390
♪ Didn’t get to say I love you so much ♪

838
00:43:13,480 --> 00:43:17,920
♪ You broke into my lonely heart ♪

839
00:43:17,940 --> 00:43:21,750
♪ And lit the fire called love ♪

840
00:43:21,770 --> 00:43:26,110
♪ You drove out all my loneliness ♪

841
00:43:26,130 --> 00:43:29,580
♪ So that I can slowly adjust myself ♪

842
00:43:30,080 --> 00:43:34,260
♪ You painted my life ♪

843
00:43:34,280 --> 00:43:37,930
♪ With flowers ♪

844
00:43:37,950 --> 00:43:41,940
♪ You raised me up ♪

845
00:43:41,960 --> 00:43:45,430
♪ From that moment on ♪

846
00:43:45,790 --> 00:43:48,810
♪ You’ve been singing for me ♪
